The following example will show how to move to last page of the document. 

Imports System
Imports System.Windows.Forms
Imports Foxit.PDF.Viewer

Public Class Form1
    Inherits System.Windows.Forms.Form

    Private MyPdfViewer As PdfViewer

    Sub New()
